        <item>
          <versionCode>01</versionCode>
          <actionDesc>Reported to Senate amended</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Communicating Lender Activity Reports from the Small Business Administration Act or CLEAR SBA Act - Amends the Small Business Act to direct the Administrator of the Small Business Administration (SBA) to make publicly available a user-friendly database of information relating to lenders making loans under such Act or the Small Business Investment Act of 1958.</p> <p>Requires the Administrator to: (1) include in the database information on such loans made during FY2009-FY2013, and (2) incorporate information relating to such loans on an ongoing basis.</p> <p>Prohibits the Administrator from requiring lenders to submit additional information or to otherwise increase burdens on lenders in order to comply with this Act.</p> <p>Expresses the sense of Congress that no additional funds should be made available to carry out this Act.</p>]]></text>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2013-11-27T19:06:20Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <name>Reported to Senate amended</name>
          <actionDate>2013-09-10</actionDate>
          <updateDate>2013-09-10T12:54:39Z</updateDate>
        </item>
